values: General Information This is meant to be an archive of all (well, most) of the fan fiction I've written over the years. It's basically a result of my frustration at being unable to find stories I've written in the past, and while there are some stories that are still missing and assumed somewhere, it's pretty much a comprehensive collection of fan fiction I've written post-2000 (because there are some fan fiction that are so terrible that I can't even force myself to include even for archiving purposes. The stories are archived by fandom, and can be accessed through the tags on the right. The bulk of the stories are NOT archived by date, however from now on in new stories will appear at the top of each respective fandom category/subcategory. All updates will be noted as journal entries. Note: I am a slack updater. This means that stories will probably be updated in bulk when the mood strikes as opposed to any systematic or sensible order. In a certain sense, this could almost be seen more as a graveyard than a personal archive.
